1. *Nesreći* se moglo sprečiti da je bilo više pažnje. (The accident could have been prevented if there was more attention.)
2. Ova *nesreća* je ostavila dubok trag u našim životima. (This tragedy left a deep mark in our lives.)
3. *Nesreću* smo izbegli za dlaku. (We narrowly avoided the accident.)
4. Posle *nesreće*, svi su bili u šoku. (After the accident, everyone was in shock.)
5. Njegova smrt je bila prava *nesreća* za porodicu. (His death was a real tragedy for the family.)
6. Auto je bio u *nesreći* i sada moramo da ga popravimo. (The car was in an accident and now we have to fix it.)
7. Često čujemo o ljudima koji su preživeli velike *nesreće*. (We often hear about people who have survived major disasters.)
8. Oni su pretrpeli veliku *nesreću*, ali su ipak uspeli da prežive. (They suffered a great misfortune, but still managed to survive.)